I've been asked quite a few times how the "Offset strap" is much more durable
than conventional straps. 

 Here's how:

 Conventional straps: Forces acting directly on the lug screws. Thin layer of
leather wrapping around the screws.

 Offset strap: One continuous piece of leather. Almost all pulling forces are
directed under the watch. Virtually no force is acting on the lug ends. You will
have one strap that's almost impossible to break on your wrist. 

 www.offsetstraps.com

text:
We can make straps for IWC Ingenieur now!

 Like always we love to make our own stuffs.

 As the demand for IWC Ingenieur straps grows, we decide to make our own
adapters.

 The adapters are precision CNC machined from solid bronze. Bronze has high
corrosion resistance, so no worries about durability.

 Don't underestimate the time and skills involved in making these little
adapters. Not only they are CNC milled, they also undergone a process called EDM
(electrode discharge machining). EDM is mostly used in cutting parts where high
precision is needed.

 Please feel free to contact us for your custom IWC Ingenieur straps. The straps
can be made from all the materials we have such as alligator, ammo leather,
shell cordovan...and more.

 #iwcingenieur #tedsustraps #customstraps #alligatorstraps

 https://www.tedsustraps.com

 現在我們也可以製作IWC 工程師錶帶了!!

 Ted Su Straps 工作室的專長就是研發新產品，這次也不例外。

以往，都要等客人的錶帶壞掉，交給我們拆出原廠的接頭，再次做成新錶帶。

 現在有了IWC工程師錶款專用的接頭後，就不用等了! 您可以一次訂做數條錶帶，依不同場合不同心情交換錶帶使用!

 只要是我們有的皮革，都可以製作，例如短吻鱷，牛皮，古董皮，鯊魚皮...統統都可以!

 歡迎以PM聯絡我們，討論您專屬的訂製錶帶!!

#田庄私廚

 台中烏日最極致的餐廳

 極隱秘的位置，極特別的菜色，極健康的食材....和極有個人風格的林老板。

 
原本是老板招待貴賓的私人招待所，但是老板越看這個這麼棒的地方，越想分享給大家，分享安全無毒飲食的好處。他說，人到了一個年紀，累積了一定的人生體驗，最重要的就是能夠有健康的身體，和三五好友一起慢慢回味自己年輕時的豐功偉業。

 林老板父母親經營海產進口數十年，專營無毒海鮮，食材更是自行送驗，確保消費者的飲食安全。

 
今天的主角干貝飯，非常的美味，跟我們的錶帶一樣，充滿著豐富的內涵。吃了一口後，捨不得吞下肚，因為干貝的口感很扎實，越嚼越甘甜。美食節目大家都看很多，多的形容詞就不再多說，也不是我的專長。對於吃遍美食的老闆們，用心的]食材一口就可以分辯。

 餐廳在烏日交流道下來3分鐘內就可以到達，地理位置有點隱秘，但是老板說很快就會增設更多指標。

 今年九月我們就認識二十年了，林老闆，什麼時候要再請我吃好吃的干貝飯？我要多加兩顆干貝哦!

Introducing new concept from Ted Su straps: "Offset straps"

 1. The watch case is Offset away from the center line of the strap.

 "No more watch crown digging into the back of your hand".

 2. Conventional straps can break at the lug ends. A lot of force is acting on
the thin leather wrapping around the screws/spring bars. Offset straps takes
most of the force away. Virtually no force is acting on the lug ends.

 3. One piece continuous lining protects your wrist from being scratched by
watch case. Most of the un-comfortableness of watch wearing comes from the sharp
edges of watch case. In some cases, it also helps reducing allergy caused by
bronze watch case.

 4. Because of the one piece design, the heavy watch is being held and balanced
on your wrist better. Less sliding around your wrist and less unawared wrist
shacking.

 www.offsetstraps.com

28mm strap adapters for Audemars Piguet Offshore models.

 Now we can custom make leather straps for your AP Offshores with perfect fit.

 The adapters are made using a process called EDM(electrode discharge
machining). It uses thin copper wire charged with strong current to "vaporize"
and cut into materials. It's a slow and expensive machining process, but it is
ultra precise and accurate.

 Here are more info from the Wikipedia: 
https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Electrical_discharge_machining

text:
Many customers have troubles finding straps for matte black cased watches.

 Usually the better choices are matte brown cowhide such as crazy horse or
anything that's not glossy.

 I have came across this piece of very nice matte alligator. It will work very
well with these carbon or ceramic watches.

 A dark grey stitching to bring out depth of the black will be nice. Or for this
particular case, a daring blue stitching to match the second hand of this
Panerai. 

 Feel free to contact me if you are interested in having a custom strap made.

 黑色殼的手錶其實不好搭配錶帶，往往是平光(非亮面)的牛皮，例如瘋馬皮最合適，但現在我們有了一個新的選擇：
